  <steps>
    <step order="1">Load architecture §3.2, §4.4, §6.4 (flow diagram), §7.1 (Cosmos discriminator).</step>
    <step order="2">Read `MatterMemoryService.cs` to understand the Cosmos memory-container access pattern + `AppendFactAsync` signature.</step>
    <step order="3">Author `Services/Ai/Memory/IMatterMemoryPromotionService.cs` (if not already from task 088): methods `QueueForApprovalAsync`, `ApproveAsync`, `RejectAsync` returning `MatterMemoryPromotionResult` record.</step>
    <step order="4">Author `Services/Ai/Memory/MatterMemoryPromotionService.cs`:
      (a) `QueueForApprovalAsync` writes pending Cosmos doc per §6.4 schema; emits event in task 096;
      (b) `ApproveAsync` reads pending (404 → return `not_found`), calls `IMatterMemoryService.AppendFactAsync`, updates pending status to `approved` with ETag; event in task 097;
      (c) `RejectAsync` updates pending status to `rejected` with ETag; event in task 097.
    </step>
    <step order="5">Inject `IMatterMemoryService` (existing) + Cosmos client (existing, used by MatterMemoryService) + `TimeProvider` + `ILogger`.</step>
    <step order="6">Update `AiModule.cs` to register `IMatterMemoryPromotionService` → `MatterMemoryPromotionService` (concrete). If task 091 already registered the stub, replace with concrete.</step>
    <step order="7">Author unit tests at `tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Ai/Memory/MatterMemoryPromotionServiceTests.cs`:
      - Queue creates Cosmos doc with correct shape + id format
      - Approve reads pending + calls AppendFactAsync + updates status with ETag
      - Reject updates status with ETag
      - not_found returns structured result (not exception)
      - Concurrent approve attempts → ETag mismatch returns `already_resolved`
      - ADR-015 telemetry safety verified
    </step>
    <step order="8">Run `dotnet build` + `dotnet test`. Must pass.</step>
    <step order="9">Measure BFF publish-size delta; write `notes/handoffs/093-bff-publish-delta.md`.</step>
    <step order="10">Run code-review + adr-check.</step>
    <step order="11">Update TASK-INDEX.md: 093 → ✅.</step>
  </steps>

